Name: Redneck Rampage Rides Again
About the game: In this sequel to Redneck Rampage; After Leonard and Bubba crash-land a UFO, they find themselves in the middle of the desert (Area 69). Along the way, they are hunted by aliens and must blast their way through jackalope farms, Disgraceland, a riverboat, a brothel and various other locales. includes 14 new single player levels new enemies, weapons, and vehicles, including motorcycles and swamp boats
